Regular bench made of wood
for two people.

Bench made of stone.
Very solid looking.

Classy bench made with
rubies. Glittering red
gives a touch of luxury.

Classy bench made with
emeralds.
Glittering green goes
great with spring foliage.

Classy bench made with
adamantite.
Glittering blue to soothe
your soul.

Classy bench made with
topaz.
Glittering yellow goes
great with ginkgo trees.

Classy bench made with
agate.
Glittering pink makes it a
perfect spot for couples.

Classy bench made with
amethyst.
Glittering purple makes it
fit for royalty!

Classy bench made with
platinum.
Glittering white to make
every moment sumptuous!

Black bench made with
glittering stone.
The subtle color makes
time seem to slip away.

Classy bench made with
gold.
Glittering gold for that
lavish touch!

Classy bench made with
silver.
Glittering silver for that
elegant atmosphere!

Wooden barrel.
Handy in the garden.

Wooden box, big enough for
a person to fit inside!

Rustic mannequin stands in
fields and paddies to
scare away birds and
pests.

Attach it to the roof of a
building and it will show
which way the wind is
blowing!

Milk can made of silver.
Originally for holding
milk from cows, but this
is just for decoration.

Hay rolled up in a bundle.
Placed out in the fields,
it creates a bucolic
atmosphere!

Who piled up these bricks?
When? Why?
Is something going to be
made from these later?

Expensive pot made of
ruby.

Expensive blue pot made of
orichalcum.

Light and sturdy pot made
of mithril.

Not sure where this old
cart came from, but now
it's too run-down to use.

A cart used to haul people
and things, but this one
is no longer usable.

Place this fancy wagon on
the side of the road and
it will draw attention!

This where you place items
you want to ship. You get 
the money automatically
the next day.

A section of narrow road
with a few weeds.

A section of road paved
with stones.

A section of road paved
with brick.

Lay this on the ground to
set apart an area from its
surroundings.

Large paving stones to
create wide roads.

A light on a tall pole to
light the road at night.
Place in park or garden so
you can go at night, too!

A fancy street light with
two decorative lights to
illuminate the town at
night.

Iron basket that holds
burning firewood for
outdoor illumination.

Oil burns inside a papered
wood frame. A traditional
means of lighting in some
countries.

A stone lantern as seen in
Eastern temples. Doesn't
light up... Just for
show in Eastern gardens.
Pillar made of wood.
Pillar made of stone.

Pillar made of brick, with
contrasting colors that
look nice in a garden.

Pillar carved in ethnic
style. Kind of small.

Large carved wood pillar
with traditional ethnic
designs.

Iron table in the Western
style, suitable for a
Western garden.

Wood table in the Eastern
style, suitable for an
Eastern garden.

Table in a traditional
tropical style.

Iron chair in the Western
style, suitable for a
Western garden.

Chair for having tea
outdoors. Red felt cover
over a wooden base.

Charmingly rustic chair
made from a log.

Comfy reclining chair like
you see at a beach resort.

A set of wood table and
three chairs under a large
yellow sun umbrella.

A large red sun umbrella
for having tea outdoors.
A large version of a
parasol you would carry.

A large umbrella to keep
the sun off, like you see
at beach resorts.

A board with something
written on it, affixed to
a stake...like a small
signboard.

Stands at intersections or
forks in the road to show
people where the road
goes.

Small signboard that
stands in front of a shop,
telling its name and menu.

Legend says this statue is
a faithful dog that waited
so long for its master, it
turned to stone.

A statue that contains the
energy of the sun!
Said to possess amazing
power.

Her spear is said to
pierce any shield. Part of
a pair with the statue of
a maiden with shield.

Her shield is said to turn
away any spear. Part of a
pair with the statue of a
maiden with spear.

Fountain of water flowing
from a bird's mouth. In a
park, makes a nice spot
for kids to play in.

Ordinary square fountain,
with cool and refreshing
water bubbling out.

Lavish fountain with a
female statue. The water
ever-flowing from her pot
is a symbol of abundance.

A set of pond and small
girder bridge.

A set of pond and small
arch bridge.

A deep, deep well that
never runs dry. You can
draw water from it with a
watering can.

A decorative minecart that
creates a mine-like
atmosphere.

A stone tower that lets
you see a long way.

A small plaza made of
wood. Add a bench and it
makes a nice rest stop for
people strolling by.

Small plaza paved with
stones. Add interesting
amenities to make it a
town highlight.

Small plaza paved with
brick. Add potted plants
and more to make it a
leisure spot for the town.

A large wooden deck-like
plaza. Place benches and
tables here and make it a
gathering place!

A plaza paved with stone.
Place artwork and
fountains to turn it into
a famous plaza...

A plaza paved with brick.
Add plants, benches and
more to make it a leisure
destination for the town.

A tool for putting out
fires. Watch out! It will
spurt out white foam if
you touch it!

A statue of a great man
who sat so long he became
like this!

In some countries these
are placed on either side
of entrances at New Year's
to bring good fortune.

A bamboo contraption that
swings up and down by
water power, making a
pleasant thump on a stone.

A weight boats drop to the
bottom of the river or sea
to stay in place.

A simple bed made of
netting, strung between
two trees.

A giant stone memorial
made by an ancient king.
Something's written on the
side in ancient writing.

Ancient tablet inscribed
with profound knowledge.
Believed to have
mysterious power...

A very fast three-wheeled
vehicle that you can ride.

A lion-shaped vehicle.
You can't get inside; you
ride by climbing on to it.
Moves pretty fast.

A panda-shaped vehicle.
You need coins to make it
move.
Not that fast-moving.

A popular character from
an old TV show.

A set with a cow statue,
stone pillar and hedge.
Fun to combine with other
amenities!

A stone crossroads with a
sheep statue and potted
flowers.

A fountain with a maiden
statue, topiary, obelisk,
and more create a classy
plaza set.

Eastern-style set with
wooden wall, parasol,
bonsai and more.

Stone slab road flanked by
bamboo groves with a pair
of stone lanterns at the
front for an Eastern look.

Arch bridge surrounded by
paper lanterns, tea table
and more make a classy,
Eastern-style set.

Ethnic-themed set with
totem pole and potted
palm trees.

Ethnic-themed set with
stone marker, totem pole,
and red pots.

Classy ethnic-style set of
sun statue, palm trees,
totem pole and more.

Small but classy set of
fancy street light and
double ball topiary.

Classy set of topiary and
wooden bench flanked by
cone trees.

Spacious and classy set of
fancy street lights,
wagon, and bench around a
lavish fountain.

Neat little park set of
street light, bench,
topiary, and more.

Spacious set of street
lights, benches,
flowerbeds and more.

Park set of arbor, stone
plaza, street lights,
benches, flowerbeds and
more.

Two trees decoratively
flanking the road.

Three large trees lining
each side of the road.

Classy set of wide tree-
lined road with benches
and streetlights.

Small garden set of bushes
adorned with flower
baskets.

Regular garden set with
bench facing hedge and
topiary.

Gazebo under a red flower
arch, parasol table,
fountain, and more make a
classy garden plaza set.

Several stalks of bamboo

Miniature version of a

A potted cherry tree with

Doesn't take up space, so

Shrub with branches
clipped nice and round.

Doesn't require care and

works well for gardening.

Shrub with branches

Shrub with branches

Shrub clipped to form a
hedge.

Shrub clipped into the

So lifelike, it looks

Shrub clipped into the

Huge and impressive!

A stand of many bamboo
plants reaching tall.
And maybe bamboo shoots on

A pine tree with beautiful
branches.
Gives a garden a peaceful
air.

A cherry tree with
beautiful flowers to

A ginkgo tree with yellow
leaves. Perfect along a
walking path.

A palm tree with tropical
pizzazz.
Doesn't produce fruit but

Wooden fencing often used
in garden design.

A statue of a cow made of

Creates a bucolic
atmosphere.

A statue of a sheep made

Creates a bucolic
atmosphere.

A statue of a chicken made
of stone and sandrose.
Creates a bucolic
atmosphere.

A statue of a horse made
of stone and sandrose.

A tin tricycle for

This watering can isn't

Spacious inside, with a

A building for animals.
Inside it are a feed box,

handy facilities.

A field of poor soil mixed

You can grow 8 crops on it

A regular field.
You can grow 8 crops on it

The best kind of field.
Crops grow better than in

A box to keep bees in so

A log to grow mushrooms

Device for making cheese,

Device for turning wool

Device that lets you mix

Device for making flours,

Use flour in recipes and

Ring the bell to call

Provides clean, fresh

Natural hot springs.
